oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好淆</blockquote><br />\n所有嘢要清晰明確<br />\n<br />\n目標：每科訂立一個短期目標，類似係要溫幾耐或者要做到幾多分<br />\n<br />\n溫習：要訂立溫習嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">時間</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">地點</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">科目</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">溫習方法</span>，越清楚越好<br />\n例如：我聽日朝早九點要開始喺屋企睇physics書，睇一個鐘之後休息十分鐘再做練習<br />\n越仔細越好，你可以用電話之類嘅嘢記低<br />\n<br />\n玩：同溫習一樣要訂時間，無乜人可以齋讀書唔玩</blockquote><br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申：當年其實無乜點用過呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係知道呢個方法普遍人都啱用</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打當年係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中六七返學上堂嗰時專心自修，禁自己瞓覺<br />\n除非有時悶得濟就搵隔離位玩同傾計（一日一兩堂左右）<br />\n放學就離開本書，返屋企會開電視睇卡通片當休息下<br />\n暑假淨係睇咗一課physics<br />\n<br />\n溫書方法：<br />\n- 齋睇幾次（要連埋思考），禁止用任何筆記抄重點，通常每次睇都會有新發現或者有嘢唔記得<br />\n- 到無再有新發現嗰時先做練習，pure maths目標係要識哂，physics目標係MC要高過90%<br />\n<br />\n好多嘢我到而家都仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5133bf44bdc51391a35cdd0598c66b78b646392d","tid":363582,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打本身底好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌撞問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麻麻地所以暑假係咁溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暑假開始溫已經贏左好撚多人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5fb7914729991a0d8282e405f32e44af56307b","tid":363582,"uid":135735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀書就一定自發既<br />\n諗下想讀咩科要幾多分</blockquote><br />\n4+1 想有24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗吓好啦傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由得我FF"},{"pid":"ea77ee2aedecf244af23a5bfdc0fc4b51c62f56f","tid":363582,"uid":96511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀書就一定自發既<br />\n諗下想讀咩科要幾多分</blockquote><br />\n4+1 想有24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌想24暑假仲咁hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身底好？</blockquote><br />\n屌大家問題一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 底唔差 係得英文底差</blockquote><br />\n我都係英文出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5989752d48facd9797273e14eaf82bb286f1d991","tid":363582,"uid":69013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"1.早睡早起<br />\n2.搵全班最勤力最高分最樂於助人嘅同學一齊溫，做練習睇完solution 對完有咩唔明問下佢<br />\n3.有d人屋企溫得專心，有d人係study room 溫得專心，睇下你係咩人<br />\n4.認真，做練習/PP要留底，要對solution 幫自己改一次，用紅筆記低自己錯邊，得閒拎番本練習/PP睇下自己答錯咩，睇睇下就記得晒<br />\n<br />\n當年我AL從來無死背過書，靠理解同睇得多；但有d人天生記性好好，背2次就記得晒。如果你記性好，我建議直接硬背，溫得會比較快。"},{"pid":"61fc381fb2b54dab53e2f0d94722d0668a703730","tid":363582,"uid":96511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打本身底好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌撞問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麻麻地所以暑假係咁溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暑假開始溫已經贏左好撚多人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁同自己講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過之前太hea 追翻都要d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bae0d3a33f85c26c5b101e5facb4211610f628","tid":363582,"uid":135735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>入唔到大學咁會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又冇話一定要入嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但始終唔想考咁差 面對唔到自己同唔想曬9父母辛辛苦苦賺比我嗰啲補習費 同埋下年考18dse嘅人仲多過以往幾千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好淆</blockquote><br />\n所有嘢要清晰明確<br />\n<br />\n目標：每科訂立一個短期目標，類似係要溫幾耐或者要做到幾多分<br />\n<br />\n溫習：要訂立溫習嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">時間</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">地點</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">科目</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">溫習方法</span>，越清楚越好<br />\n例如：我聽日朝早九點要開始喺屋企睇physics書，睇一個鐘之後休息十分鐘再做練習<br />\n越仔細越好，你可以用電話之類嘅嘢記低<br />\n<br />\n玩：同溫習一樣要訂時間，無乜人可以齋讀書唔玩</blockquote><br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申：當年其實無乜點用過呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係知道呢個方法普遍人都啱用</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打當年係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中六七返學上堂嗰時專心自修，禁自己瞓覺<br />\n除非有時悶得濟就搵隔離位玩同傾計（一日一兩堂左右）<br />\n放學就離開本書，返屋企會開電視睇卡通片當休息下<br />\n暑假淨係睇咗一課physics<br />\n<br />\n溫書方法：<br />\n- 齋睇幾次（要連埋思考），禁止用任何筆記抄重點，通常每次睇都會有新發現或者有嘢唔記得<br />\n- 到無再有新發現嗰時先做練習，pure maths目標係要識哂，physics目標係MC要高過90%<br />\n<br />\n好多嘢我到而家都仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f082c342b1286d9a9b36359afa27b57337db03","tid":363582,"uid":135735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.早睡早起<br />\n2.搵全班最勤力最高分最樂於助人嘅同學一齊溫，做練習睇完solution 對完有咩唔明問下佢<br />\n3.有d人屋企溫得專心，有d人係study room 溫得專心，睇下你係咩人<br />\n4.認真，做練習/PP要留底，要對solution 幫自己改一次，用紅筆記低自己錯邊，得閒拎番本練習/PP睇下自己答錯咩，睇睇下就記得晒<br />\n<br />\n當年我AL從來無死背過書，靠理解同睇得多；但有d人天生記性好好，背2次就記得晒。如果你記性好，我建議直接硬背，溫得會比較快。</blockquote><br />\n早睡早起真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a397a4c0b1eb9c2f4878a639e68fefe43eebbe","tid":363582,"uid":78703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:23:35.000Z","msg":"飲杯可樂打下機仲好啦"},{"pid":"3e7ed8d5ebe72d334f2e17c10e72826822121eed","tid":363582,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}